paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
select categoryGroup, count(distinct subOrderId) as orders from (
Select distinct o.subOrderId, a.categoryGroup 
From (select orderDate, subOrderId from `temp.Order_Att` where lower(utmCampaign) = lower('YT_TrueView_Generic_Influencer_CPT_7D_03112022') and orderDate > '2022-11-03' order by orderDate) o
left join (select distinct subOrderId, categoryGroup from `all(agCmDump)` where TO_DATE(FROM_UNIXTIME(orderDate/1000))>'2022-11-03') a
on o.subOrderId=a.subOrderId) tb group by categoryGroup order by orders DESC
",1000)
